State Regulations
(a) Route 70. Route
70 between the Allegany-Steuben county line and the western village line of

between Route 19 (South Main Street) and the Allegany-Steuben county line in
the Villages of Wellsville and Andover and the Towns of Wellsville and

Andover. Notes
